* RC Circuit Transient Response

*resistor connected between node 1 & 2
R1 1 2 1k

*capacitor connected between nodes 2 & 0
C1 2 0 1u

*piecewise linear input voltage
vin 1 0 pwl (0 0 10ms 0 11ms 5v  20ms 5v)

*transient analysis for 20ms, step size 0.02ms
.tran 0.02ms 20ms

*define run-time control functions
.control
run

*plotting I/O voltages 
plot v(1) v(2)

*export simulation as csv file 
write output.csv V(1)
.endc
.end
